Package: dryadAPI
Title: Package to interact with the dryad data repository 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Thorben", "Kurzbach", , "tkurzbac@uthsc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-0264-9604"))
Description: 
Provides convenient R functions to interact with the Dryad data repository (https://datadryad.org). 
This package allows users to programmatically search for datasets, retrieve metadata, download files, 
and import data directly into the R environment. Designed to support reproducible research and facilitate 
access to open scientific datasets.
